Wind drives @@yyellow@@N grit in low ribbons while @@bbrown@@N retaining walls keep the lane coherent despite branching footpaths.@@N
From this square, gulls track the hidden waterline somewhere ahead, and every marker suggests traders once moved in disciplined columns.@@N
Fresh sandal tracks cross older hoof marks and vanish at the next bend.@@N
A broken plinth bears a precise stepped-triangle emblem, hinting at a sealed pyramid road still waiting to be opened.@@N
~
